# Models Directory

This directory stores generated model files.

## Generate Models

Run these scripts to generate the required model files:

```bash
python scripts/generate_embeddings.py
python scripts/train_clustering.py
```

This will create:
- `embeddings.pkl` (~29 MB) - Document embeddings
- `clusters.pkl` (~3 MB) - Clustering model

These files are required for the API to run but are not committed to git due to their size.
